 Unity 强烈反对解释：为什么游戏开发者在 Twitter 上发声https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-backlash-explained-why-game-developers-are-speaking-out-on-twitter-3497816?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=unity-backlash-解释了为什么游戏开发者在 Twitter 上发声Imogen DonovanThu, 14 Sep 2023 10:03:13 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3497816 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> 《Cult Of The Lamb》等工作室批评了游戏引擎定价的有争议的变化</p><p><a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-backlash-explained-why-game-developers-are-speaking-out-on-twitter-3497816">Unity 的强烈反对帖子解释了：为什么游戏开发者在 Twitter 上发声</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/unity">Unity</a>的新收费—— <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-developers-criticise-unity-for-baffling-new-fees-3497182">每次安装游戏时都会向开发者收取</a>费用——已经引起了那些使用软件引擎谋生的人的愤怒。</p><ul><li><strong>了解更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/gaming-features/why-steam-next-fests-demos-are-a-vital-celebration-of-gamings-future-3459650">为什么 Steam Next Fest 的演示是对游戏未来的重要庆祝</a></strong></li></ul><p>9 月 12 日公布的运行时费用将于 2024 年 1 月 1 日起生效。从该日期起，每当玩家下载符合资格的游戏时，开发者都将被收取费用。</p><p> <a href="https://blog.unity.com/news/plan-pricing-and-packaging-updates?utm_source=twitter&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=company_global_blog_2023-09-12_twitter-update-13" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unity 通过解释 Unity 引擎分为两个部分来证明这一点</a>：Unity 编辑器和 Unity 运行时。由于每次安装游戏时，也会安装支持 Unity Runtime 的代码，该公司正在通过这些新费用寻求双方之间的“正确的价值交换”。</p><p>然而，只有当游戏达到两个标准后，才会触发费用。一旦游戏年收入达到 200,000 美元或以上，并且自发布以来已安装至少 200,000 次，使用 Unity Personal 和 Unity Plus 的用户将被收取费用。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497889" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497889" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3497889" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-backlash-cult-of-the-lamb-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497889" class="wp-caption-text"> 《杀戮尖塔》来源：Humble Bundle</figcaption></figure><p> Unity Pro 和 Unity Enterprise 订阅者必须从其游戏中获得 100 万美元或以上的年收入，并且自游戏推出以来已安装至少 100 万次。</p><p>开发商，尤其是规模较小的开发商，对新的定价计划犹豫不决。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/strange-scaffold">Strange Scaffold</a>创始人 Xalavier Nelson Jr. <a href="https://twitter.com/WritNelson/status/1701720278189937099" target="_blank" rel="noopener">分享道</a>：“我听说至少有一个重要的开发者团体正在谈论针对 Unity 的集体诉讼。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/slay-the-spire"><em>《Slay The Spire》</em></a>的开发商<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/mega-crit">Mega Crit</a><a href="https://twitter.com/MegaCrit/status/1702077576209207611" target="_blank" rel="noopener">将运行时费用描述为“违反信任”</a> ，并宣布如果运行时费用仍然存在，它将把下一款游戏迁移到新引擎。 “我们之前从未发表过公开声明。这就是你搞砸的程度。”它总结道。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/massive-monster">Massive Monster</a>还威胁称将于 2024 年 1 月 1 日删除<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/cult-of-the-lamb"><em>《Cult Of The Lamb》</em></a> ， <a href="https://x.com/cultofthelamb/status/1701715971663425897?s=20" target="_blank" rel="noopener">以抗议 Unity 新的定价计划</a>。在另一份声明中，它告诉公司“ <a href="https://twitter.com/MassiveMonster/status/1701808567140102633" target="_blank" rel="noopener">别再臭了</a>”，并附上了一个邪教角色排泄粪便的动画，上面有 Unity 标志。 </p><figure id="attachment_3497200" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3497200" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3497200" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/unity-runtime-fee-debacle-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3497200" class="wp-caption-text"> Unity 徽标 图片来源：Unity</figcaption></figure><p>其他人则指出了<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/unity-bosses-sold-stock-days-before-development-fees-announcement-raising-eyebrows" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Unity首席执行官John Riccitiello选择在9月6日出售2,000股股票的时机</a>。该公司董事会成员在公告发布前出售了股票——增长总裁 Tomer Bar-Zeev 于 9 月 1 日出售了 37,500 股，董事 Shlomo Dovrat 于 8 月 30 日出售了 68,000 股。</p><p>作为回应，Unity“[承认]这种困惑和沮丧”，并在 9 月 13 日<a href="https://twitter.com/unity/status/1702077049425596900" target="_blank" rel="noopener">发布的 X 帖子中</a>重新解决了开发人员的担忧。</p><p> “我们 90% 以上的客户不会受到这一变化的影响，”它表示，并重申运行时费用只会在安装时触发一次。重新安装、演示、试用和参与筹款活动的安装将不计入总安装量。</p><p>此外，Unity 只会记录 2024 年 1 月 1 日起的净新安装量。“我们不会对欺诈性安装收取费用。对于涉嫌恶意欺诈或僵尸网络的案件，我们将直接与您合作，”它解释道。</p><p>然而，Unity 的最新帖子并没有缓解人们对价格变化的担忧。此外，其有关反欺诈措施的信息也被批评为 <a href="https://twitter.com/Andreadbx1/status/1702078916515561890" target="_blank" rel="noopener">过于模糊</a>。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/electronic-arts">艺电</a>宣布 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/the-next-sims-game-will-be-free-to-download-3497383">下一款<em>《模拟人生》</em>游戏将“免费下载”，</a>以尝试“从一开始就做<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-sims"><em>《模拟人生》</em></a>从未做过的事情”。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/unity-backlash-explained-why-game-developers-are-speaking-out-on-twitter-3497816">Unity 的强烈反对帖子解释了：为什么游戏开发者在 Twitter 上发声</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
